# Development Setup

## Prerequisites

- Python {{ min_python_version }} or higher
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)
- [mise](https://mise.jdx.dev/)
- [make](https://www.gnu.org/software/make/) (optional, wraps mise tasks)
{%- if dockerfile %}
- [Docker](https://www.docker.com/) (optional, for containerized development)
{%- endif %}
{%- if with_doppler %}
- [Doppler](https://www.doppler.com/) (for secrets management)
{%- endif %}

## Getting Started

Clone the repository and install dependencies:

```bash
git clone {{ repository }}
cd {{ project_name }}
```

/// tab | make
```bash
make setup-dev
```
///

/// tab | mise
```bash
mise run setup:dev
```
///

## Common Tasks

| Task | make | mise |
|------|------|------|
| Run tests | `make test` | `mise run test` |
| Run linting & type checks | `make check-all` | `mise run check:all` |
| Format code | `make format` | `mise run format` |
| Serve docs locally | `make docs-serve` | `mise run docs:serve` |
| Build the package | `make build` | `mise run build` |

> For the full list of available tasks, see the [Task Runner](task-runner.md) guide.
